data.title: About: U.S. Music Corporation
data.meta_description: U.S. Music Corp. is an American musical instrument company based in Buffalo Grove, Illinois, United States, a suburb of Chicago, that manufactures and distributes products worldwide. The company is currently an independent subsidiary of multinational corporate group Exertis | JAM.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

U.S. Music Corp. is an American musical instrument company based in Buffalo Grove, Illinois, United States, a suburb of Chicago, that manufactures and distributes products worldwide. The company is currently an independent subsidiary of multinational corporate group Exertis | JAM. (en)
